301	---
302	
303	## Mock Factory Management
304	
305	### Using Existing Factories
306	
307	```typescript
308	import {
309	  createMockUser,
310	  createMockOrganization,
311	  createMockMembership,
312	  createMockJob,
313	} from "@/test-utils/factories";
314	
315	// With defaults
316	const user = createMockUser();
317	
318	// With overrides
319	const user = createMockUser({
320	  email: "specific@example.com",
321	  role: "admin",
322	});
323	```
324	
325	### Creating New Factories
326	
327	When new factories are needed, add to `src/test-utils/factories/`:
328	
329	```typescript
330	// Add to src/test-utils/factories/<model-name>.ts
331	export interface NewEntityRecord {
332	  id: string;
333	  organizationId: string;
334	  name: string;
335	  status: "ACTIVE" | "INACTIVE";
336	  createdAt: Date;
337	  updatedAt: Date;
338	}
339	
340	const DEFAULT_DATE = new Date("2026-01-01T00:00:00Z");
341	
342	export function createMockNewEntity(overrides: Partial<NewEntityRecord> = {}): NewEntityRecord {
343	  return {
344	    id: "ne_test_default",
345	    organizationId: testOrgId(),
346	    name: "Test Entity",
347	    status: "ACTIVE",
348	    createdAt: DEFAULT_DATE,
349	    updatedAt: DEFAULT_DATE,
350	    ...overrides,
351	  };
352	}
353	
354	// Then export from src/test-utils/factories/index.ts
355	// Then update docs/SERVICE_INVENTORY.md
356	```
357	
358	---
359	
360	## Required Test Cases Checklist
361	
362	For each method, ensure:
363	
364	- [ ] Happy path (normal operation)
365	- [ ] Invalid input (validation errors)
366	- [ ] Missing resource (not found)
367	- [ ] Permission denied (auth failures)
368	- [ ] External failure (API/DB errors)
369	- [ ] Edge cases (null, empty, boundary values)
370	- [ ] 100% line/branch/function/statement coverage
371	- [ ] All mock data uses shared factories from `src/test-utils/factories/`
372	- [ ] No `as any` in tests (use `as never` for DI wiring)
373	- [ ] No inline mock objects that duplicate factory shapes
374	- [ ] SERVICE_INVENTORY.md updated for new factories
375	
376	---
377	
378	## BEADS Integration
379	
380	```bash
